**None found.** The orchestrator has zero cache optimization or model compatibility logic. No interaction with pi-cache-optimizer. No prompt rewrite, no cache stats, no compatibility warnings.

### 5. pi-cache-optimizer `before_agent_start` (lines 4110-4200)

```typescript
// Lines ~4110-4200 (simplified)
pi.on("before_agent_start", async (event, _ctx) => {
  // 1. OpenAI Responses API bypass — skip all prompt modifications
  if (model && isResponsesPromptRewriteBypassApi(model.api)) return {};

  // 2. Runtime guard + global opt-out (NO_PROMPT_REWRITE env)
  if (!runtimeOptimizerEnabled) return {};
  if (isEnabledEnv(process.env[NO_PROMPT_REWRITE_ENV])) return {};

  // 3. Strip per-turn churn from <session-overview>
  const strippedPrompt = stripSessionOverviewChurn(event.systemPrompt);

  // 4. Compress skills XML → one-line index
  const compressedPrompt = compressSkillsInSystemPrompt(strippedPrompt, event.systemPromptOptions);

  // 5. Stable prefix reorder with integrity guard
  const optimized = optimizeSystemPrompt(compressedPrompt, event.systemPromptOptions);

  // Returns modified systemPrompt if changed, else compressed/stripped original
  if (optimized.changed && ...) return { systemPrompt: optimized.systemPrompt };
  if (compressedPrompt !== strippedPrompt) return { systemPrompt: compressedPrompt };
  if (strippedPrompt !== event.systemPrompt) return { systemPrompt: strippedPrompt };
  return {};
});
```

Also: `before_provider_request` injects `prompt_cache_key` for OpenAI-compatible APIs.

### 6. pi-cache-optimizer compression + reorder (lines 470-600)

- **`stripSessionOverviewChurn()`** (470-531): Regex-based removal of RECENT COMMITS, Working directory, Line count from `<session-overview>`
- **`optimizeSystemPrompt()`** (531-600): `buildStableCandidates()` → extract stable prefix parts → reorder as `stablePrefix + "\n\n---\n\n" + rest`. Integrity guard checks XML tags + HTML comment markers.

